name: Ancient Tablets of King Femi: Amber
description:
Buried to the Northern Hills.
Surrounded by volcanic rock.
The red thick ooze of heat runs around its path.
Wisdom of Wizards.
Hacks of the ancient brains.
Far beyond this world of possibilities.
The Amber tablet is the door to finding what the role of Magik has in this realm.
Only a certain hand may touch it.
All who knows, feel the burn with no need to glance upon it.
